::Mosquitor::

The CR tank completes its repairs, releasing Mosquitor. The bug steps out, 
tripping over the rim as he does so and falling on his face. He looks up, 
getting to his feet and recieving the transmission from Decadel.

Mosquitor walks to the exit, gun ready just in case. He looks threateningly 
at Decadel as he reaches the exit. This bug wasn't about to be tricked again.
